## Team & keys

- Add a teammate (admin only): `optikk users add dev@example.com --role member`
  — without `--password`, the server emails them a set-password link.
- List members: `optikk users list --agent`.
- Rotate the ingest key: `optikk keys rotate --agent` (the old key can keep
  working for up to 5 minutes).

